My KSP won't get past a black "Loading..." screen as soon as I start up the 64bit .exe, I updated it through the patcher to 1.1.1 though.

Here's the log: http://pastebin.com/15uw2FaY

Edited May 1, 2016 by Tortoise
To eliminate patcher screwups (it's only just been resurrected) and file corruption, the first thing to try would be a fresh download of 1.1.1. (or wait for 1.1.2, soon now).
Have you tried clearing the contents of .config/unity3d ?
I don't know where that folder is @v8Dave, but I went ahead with steve_v's solution and it's now solved. Thank you.
